aVHe determined to take a walk about the village.
p2861
aVThis was his usual\u000acustom on arriving in a new place.
p2862
aVOn such occasions he kept his eyes\u000aopen, and looked about, in the hope that he might somewhere see the\u000aobject of his search.
p2863
aVHe little suspected that Tony was at that very\u000amoment in the stable-yard in the rear of the hotel.
