aVBut I should be ashamed if I had not left that kind\u000aof life as soon as I was able."
p4897
aV"By Heaven, you shall go back to it!"
p4898
aVsaid Rudolph, malignantly.
p4899
aV"I never will," answered Tony, gently, but firmly.
p4900
