p6084
aVThe story is told in that\u000aentertaining way which has made Mr. Alger's name a household word in so\u000amany homes.
p6085
aV+Birdie+: A Tale of Child Life.
p6086
aVBy H. L.\u000a     CHILDE-PEMBERTON.
p6087
aVIllustrated by H. W. RAINEY.
p6088
aV12mo,\u000a     cloth, price 75 cents.
p6089
aV"The story is quaint and simple, but there is a freshness about it\u000a     that makes one hear again the ringing laugh and the cheery shout\u000a     of children at play which charmed his earlier years."
p6090
