p7344
aV"I think," said I angrily, "that they are Little Devils.
p7345
aVThat black\u000aman was a man.
p7346
aVIf they had given him half a chance--"\u000a\u000a"Remember," said my heathen friend, quite calmly, "that I do not know\u000ayour black man, or what they did to him.
p7347
aVSomething unpleasant, it\u000aappears.
p7348
aVIt does not matter.
p7349
aVIt is in the Game.
