p7486
aV'Why should he mean harm to me?'
p7487
aV"'He is the _pariente_--the relative--of Don Augusto,' I said.
p7488
aVMy\u000ateniente looked at me, and I saw that he did not like to hear the\u000aname of Don Augusto.
