p10347
aVI got 'em for him.
p10348
aVThe little beggar\u000awas so glad he gave me a hundred, and I played it on the twelve at\u000aRafferty's--there were twelve trees--and the twelve came.
p10349
aVThey\u000awouldn't let me bet again, so I came up to Manila."
p10350
aV"Hell," said the aged young man apathetically, "what's thirty-six\u000ahundred?
p10351
aVI could cash up that myself."
p10352
