p13419
aVWhat had happened, however, on this particular afternoon was that Dolff\u000ahad seen them from a window, and had sallied forth to join them.
p13420
aVDolff\u000ahad a very comfortable little study to which he retired for certain\u000ahours in the day \u201cto work\u201d--as everybody said.
p13421
